- Plans
  - Status:
    - `âœ… Completed` - Work finished, document archived
    - `â³ In Progress` - Actively being worked on
    - `ğŸ“ Draft` - Initial draft, not reviewed
    - `ğŸ—„ï¸ Archived` - Historical, no longer maintained
    - `ğŸ”„ Under Review` - Awaiting review/approval
    - `âŒ Deprecated` - Superseded by newer document
    - `ğŸ¯ Proposed` - Proposed but not approved
  - Locations:
    - Plans: `.ai/plans/<plan_name>.md`
    - Phases: `.ai/plans/phases/<plan_name>.phase-<phase_number>.md`
  - Plan phases exist as individual markdown documents.
  - Plan Lifecycle
    - Draft: The Exploratory / Pre-Planning phase
    - Proposal: The plan has been selected from options, and is not finalized
    - Creation:
      - Determine if the work should extend an existing plan or start a new one
      - Update the INDEX.md to include the Plan, and component phases
  - Phase Lifecycle
    - Start
      - Update the status in the phase & plan documents
    - Complete
      - Update the status in the phase & plan documents
